# Church & Code

> Catholic perspectives on AI ethics. A reference site for the AI moment, written for tech-curious readers and Catholic ones alike. Every page is sourced to primary documents where possible.

This site provides citation-grade reference content on Catholic teaching about artificial intelligence, organized into topical clusters. Pope Leo XIV has made AI the defining theme of his papacy, drawing explicit parallels to Pope Leo XIII's response to the Industrial Revolution in *Rerum Novarum* (1891).

